# Copy to .env.local (or set in Cloudflare Pages env vars) to enable the
# early-access form to POST to a real endpoint. Any service that accepts a
# JSON POST works (e.g. Formspree: https://formspree.io/f/XXXXXXXX).
#
# When this is empty/unset, the early-access form gracefully falls back to a
# prefilled mailto link, so no submission is ever lost.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORM_ENDPOINT=
